#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:2
msgid "反序列化"
msgstr "Unserialization"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:5
msgid "PHP序列化实现"
msgstr "PHP Serialization Implementation"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:8
msgid "常见处理器"
msgstr "Common Handlers"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:9
msgid ""
"PHP序列化处理共有几种，分别为php、php_serialize、php_binary和WDDX(需要编译时开启支持)，默认为php，可通过配置中的"
" ``session.serialize_handler`` 修改。"
msgstr ""
"PHP has several serialization handlers: php, php_serialize, php_binary, and "
"WDDX (which requires support enabled at compile time). The default is php, "
"and it can be changed with ``session.serialize_handler`` in the configuration."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:11
msgid ""
"如果 PHP 编译时加入了 WDDX 支持，则只能用 WDDX，WDDX从PHP 7.4版本后开始弃用。从 PHP 5.5.4 起可以使用 "
"php_serialize。 php_serialize 在内部简单地直接使用 serialize/unserialize 函数，并且不会有 "
"php 和 php_binary 所具有的限制。"
msgstr ""
"If PHP was compiled with WDDX support, only WDDX can be used. WDDX has been "
"deprecated since PHP 7.4. php_serialize can be used starting with PHP 5.5.4. "
"Internally, php_serialize simply uses the serialize/unserialize functions "
"directly and does not have the limitations of php and php_binary."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:13
msgid "其中PHP处理器的格式为：键名 + 竖线 + 经过serialize()函数序列化处理的值。"
msgstr "The PHP handler format is: key name + vertical bar + value serialized by serialize()."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:15
msgid "其中php_binary处理器的格式为：键名的长度对应的 ASCII 字符 + 键名 + 经过serialize()函数序列化处理的值。"
msgstr "The php_binary handler format is: ASCII character corresponding to the key name length + key name + value serialized by serialize()."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:17
msgid "其中php_serialize处理器的格式为：经过serialize()函数序列化处理的数组。"
msgstr "The php_serialize handler format is: an array serialized by serialize()."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:20
msgid "序列化格式"
msgstr "Serialization Format"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:21
msgid ""
"其中php_serialize的实现在 ``php-src/ext/standard/var.c`` 中，主要函数为 "
"``php_var_serialize_intern`` ，序列化后的格式如下："
msgstr ""
"php_serialize is implemented in ``php-src/ext/standard/var.c``. The main "
"function is ``php_var_serialize_intern``, and the serialized format is as "
"follows:"

