msgstr "``O:1:\"A\":2:{s:1:\"a\";i:1;s:1:\"b\";R:2;}``"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:45
msgid "``$a = new A();$a->a=1;$a->b=&$a->a;``"
msgstr "``$a = new A();$a->a=1;$a->b=&$a->a;``"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:48
msgid "private与protect"
msgstr "private and protect"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:49
msgid "private与protect变量和public变量不同，不能直接设置。"
msgstr "private and protect variables differ from public variables and cannot be set directly."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:51
#, python-format
msgid "private属性只能在其被定义的类内部访问，且不会被继承，在属性前加上类名，即 ``%00className%00`` 用于标定其是私有的。"
msgstr "private properties can only be accessed inside the class where they are defined and are not inherited. Prefixing the property with the class name, namely ``%00className%00``, marks it as private."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:53
msgid "protected属性可以在父类和子类中访问，变量前添加 ``%00*%00`` 用于标定其是受保护的。"
msgstr "protected properties can be accessed in parent and child classes. Prefixing the variable with ``%00*%00`` marks it as protected."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:56
msgid "PHP反序列化漏洞"
msgstr "PHP Unserialization Vulnerabilities"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:57
msgid ""
"php在反序列化的时候会调用 ``__wakeup`` / ``__sleep`` "
"等函数，可能会造成代码执行等问题。若没有相关函数，在析构时也会调用相关的析构函数，同样会造成代码执行。"
msgstr ""
"During unserialization, PHP calls functions such as ``__wakeup`` / "
"``__sleep``, which may lead to code execution and related issues. If those "
"functions are absent, related destructors may still be called during "
"destruction, which can also lead to code execution."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:59
msgid "另外 ``__toString`` / ``__call`` 两个函数也有利用的可能。"
msgstr "The ``__toString`` / ``__call`` functions may also be exploitable."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:61
msgid ""
"其中 ``__wakeup`` 在反序列化时被触发，``__destruct`` 在GC时被触发， ``__toString`` "
"在echo时被触发, ``__call`` 在一个未被定义的函数调用时被触发。"
msgstr ""
"``__wakeup`` is triggered during unserialization, ``__destruct`` is triggered "
"during GC, ``__toString`` is triggered during echo, and ``__call`` is "
"triggered when an undefined function is called."

