#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:147
msgid "利用点"
msgstr "Exploitation Points"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:150
msgid "SoapClient 原生利用"
msgstr "SoapClient Native Exploitation"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:151
msgid "php中的SoapClient类可以创建soap数据报文，在非wsdl模式下，SoapClient的实例反序列化的时候会对第二个参数指明的url进行soap请求，该特性可用于SSRF。"
msgstr "The SoapClient class in PHP can create SOAP messages. In non-WSDL mode, when a SoapClient instance is unserialized, it sends a SOAP request to the URL specified by the second parameter. This behavior can be used for SSRF."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:154
msgid "ZipArchive 原生利用"
msgstr "ZipArchive Native Exploitation"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:155
msgid ""
"php原生类 ``ZipArchive::open()`` 中的flag参数如果设置为  ``ZipArchive::OVERWRITE`` "
"时，会删除指定文件，该特性在一定条件下可以用于删除文件。"
msgstr ""
"If the flag parameter of PHP's native ``ZipArchive::open()`` is set to "
"``ZipArchive::OVERWRITE``, the specified file is deleted. Under certain "
"conditions, this behavior can be used to delete files."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:158
msgid "Session"
msgstr "Session"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:159
msgid "PHP中session默认是以文件形式存储的，文件以sess_sessionid命名，在session一定程度可控的情况下，可通过session触发反序列化。"
msgstr "In PHP, sessions are stored as files by default, with filenames in the form sess_sessionid. When the session is controllable to some extent, unserialization can be triggered through the session."

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:162
msgid "相关CVE"
msgstr "Related CVEs"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:165
msgid "CVE-2016-7124"
msgstr "CVE-2016-7124"

#: ../../source/language/php/unserialize.rst:166
msgid "在PHP 5.6.25 之前版本和 7.0.10 之前的版本，当对象的属性(变量)数大于实际的个数时， ``__wakeup()`` 不会被执行。"
msgstr "In versions before PHP 5.6.25 and before 7.0.10, when the number of object properties (variables) is greater than the actual count, ``__wakeup()`` is not executed."
